# Artifacts produced while running the scripted example projects.
# These are generated on the fly by `javah` (headers), `nativeInit` (build files)
# and the native build tools (compiled libraries). Keeping the examples pristine
# ensures every scripted run starts from scratch.
#
# NOTE: CMakeLists.txt is intentionally NOT ignored — some examples (e.g. multiclasses)
# ship a hand-written one. Generated CMakeLists.txt only ever live in the scripted
# temp copy, never in these sources.

# javah-generated JNI headers
**/include/

# nativeInit-generated build files
Cargo.toml
meson.build
meson.options

# compiled native libraries
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll
